This is a term used to describe people born in a particular period of time,

88
00:04:50,399 --> 00:04:54,079
usually but not always a period of about 18 to 20 years.

89
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:57,359
And we were focusing on generation Z or Gen Z,

90
00:04:57,359 --> 00:04:59,839
which includes those born in the early naughties,

91
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:05,599
which is the first decade of the 21st century from 2000 to 2009.

92
00:05:05,599 --> 00:05:08,399
The next expression was 2k2 for.

93
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:13,120
This means to provide something that is needed or wanted for a particular group.

94
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:17,840
And if you're trying to sell something, you need to cater for your target market.

95
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:21,840
And if your market is Gen Z, you need to be aware that they are tech-inate,

96
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,280
hyper-informed.

97
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:27,040
They've grown up with connected technology and are very knowledgeable.

98
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,840
And this makes them extremely savvy.

99
